Dear Investor,

In light of recent events in the US banking ecosystem involving Silicon Val=
ley Bank, Signature Bank, First Republic, One Bank, and Western Alliance, w=
e would like to assure you that Faropoint and its Funds remain unaffected.

Neither Faropoint nor its Funds hold capital in any of the aforementioned b=
anks and therefore have no exposure to recent affairs.

In the wake of the first SVB rumors, we reviewed all deposits managed by Fa=
ropoint in detail, and we are currently working to further diversify those =
deposits among the largest and most stabilized banks.

Faropoint continues to be an advocate of diversification, and once again, w=
e meet the importance of diversifying capital and risk.

Finally, we would like to mention that our main investments are in the form=
 of brick and mortar, and our cash and deposits are comparably insignifican=
t.

We hope the banking environment will swiftly pass, and that stabilization a=
nd trust will be regained.

As always, we are available for you.

All the best,

Faropoint team


Faropoint Office


Tel: +972-3-7710111 | Fax : +972-3-7714207
7 Derech Menahem Begin St,
Ramat Gan, Israel

