<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Dear Investor,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">In light of recent events in the US banking ecosyste=
m involving Silicon Valley Bank, Signature Bank, First Republic, One Bank, =
and Western Alliance, we would like to assure you that
<b>Faropoint and its Funds remain unaffected.<o:p></o:p></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Neither Faropoint nor its Funds hold capital in any =
of the aforementioned banks and therefore have no exposure to recent affair=
s.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">In the wake of the first SVB rumors, we reviewed all=
 deposits managed by Faropoint in detail, and we are currently working to f=
urther diversify those deposits among the largest and most stabilized banks=
.
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Faropoint continues to be an advocate of diversifica=
tion, and once again, we meet the importance of diversifying capital and ri=
sk.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Finally, we would like to mention that our main inve=
stments are in the form of brick and mortar, and our cash and deposits are =
comparably insignificant.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We hope the banking environment will swiftly pass, a=
nd that stabilization and trust will be regained.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
